"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-uk-1884061-team-gb-union-jack-row-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GB has revealed its athletes will wear a traditional Union Jack on their kits when it comes to this summer's Olympic Games - after an \\\"inclusive\\\" flag was used on merchandise.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9989236838998407, \"rank\": 0.0006565105639385557, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993977357182982, \"rank\": 0.0005869236462908026, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9936072020385149, \"rank\": 0.004853384231841046, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement came after Team GB was on the receiving end of backlash for an artsy flag it used on selected pieces of memorabilia.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9989236838998407, \"rank\": 0.0006565105639385557, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bath-based agency Thisaway came up with the concept in an attempt to 'find a way of refreshing Team GB's colour palette'.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9989236838998407, \"rank\": 0.0006565105639385557, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They said using the flag's colour palette was 'far from unique', prompting a backlash from politicians and the public.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Team GB has now insisted the new red-pink and blue-purple design will not feature on their kit for the Paris Olympics this summer.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9989236838998407, \"rank\": 0.0006565105639385557, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics kit was made two years ago and will be launched later this month.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Team GB slammed for 'insulting' decision to change Union flag to pink and purple    A spokesperson told Mail Sport: \\\"All Team GB athletes will wear the Union Jack as normal in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999993408437, \"rank\": 6.592222065797117e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This comes just two weeks after Nike faced backlash for its England football shirt, which changed the colours of St George's Cross on the back of the collar.\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9732950065875444, \"rank\": 0.02743639570